Aggregate Node: Roll Up Data to a Higher Level

Use an Aggregate node in CRM Analytics to roll up data. You can aggregate to a higher level of granularity or roll up hierarchical data.

Aggregate Node: Hierarchical Aggregation

Use Hierarchical Agregation in CRM Analytics to sum measures across multilevel data. For example, you can roll up revenues, assets, or liabilities for companies and their subsidiaries.
